snippet.title: Quadice - Tile-Matching Puzzle Fun! (Official Trailer)
snippet.description:
Quadice is a Tile-Matching Puzzle game that takes place in Euphionia's universe. Challenge yourself in Challenge Mode, see how high you can score in Endless Mode, or challenge others in 2-Player mode!

Buy it on itch.io:
https://euphioniaofficial.itch.io/quadice

Buy the Original Soundtrack on Bandcamp:
https://euphioniastudio.bandcamp.com/album/quadice-soundtrack-2
